description:
The remarkable Hayley Atwell (AGENT CARTER, HOWARD'S END) joins Anna and Sim for this week's episode of Unqualified! First, Hayley discusses her opinions on Los Angeles and how it differs from living in the UK. Then, Anna talks about why she loves waving at people and Hayley reflects on growing up with a particular British accent. After that, Anna and Hayley have a conversation on how success has affected their friendships before they bring up the issue surrounding the sexualization of young women. Later, Anna and Hayley audition for an imaginary restaurant reality show and play a round of deal breakers. Before the show ends, they call Jennifer, who is dealing with the aftermath of a workplace affair. Tune in and enjoy!
